ion\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\">[ἐνθάδε]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"κῖτε\">[κῖτε]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"νος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"νος\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>νος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ζήσας\">ζή[σας]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">[ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀμέμπτως\">ἀμέμπ[τως]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"τελευτᾷ\">[τελευτᾷ]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τῇ\">τῇ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"πρὸ\">πρὸ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ιδ´\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"καλανδῶν\">[καλανδῶν]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Μαρτίων\">Μαρτ(ίων)\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἡμέρᾳ\">ἡμέρ[ᾳ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\">[......\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"κῖτε\">....\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"νος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"νος\">\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ζήσας\">ΖΗ[...\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">...\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀμέμπτως\">ΑΜΕΜΠ[...\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τελευτᾷ\">.......]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τῇ\">ΤΗ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"πρὸ\">ΠΡΟ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΙΔ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"καλανδῶν\">[........]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Μαρτίων\">ΜΑΡΤ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἡμέρᾳ\">ΗΜΕΡ[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003299_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003299_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003299.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003299-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>Ferrua: [κεῖται]; Korhonen: [κῖτε]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 5\">line.5: \u003Cspan>In the lacuna, a day of the week should be mentioned\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Here lies -nos, having lived for ... years blamelessly. He died 14 days before the kalends of March on the day of…\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Qui giace -nos, avendo vissuto ... anni senza colpa. Morì 14 giorni prima delle Calende di marzo, nel giorno di …\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>This Christian epitaph has the traditional structure with the \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐνθάδε κεῖται\u003C/span> formula, the name of the deceased (here in the lacuna) followed by his age and by another independent sentence with the day of death (with the present of \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω\u003C/span>), as recurring in other inscriptions from Catania, such as IG 14.556 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001375\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001375\u003C/a>. In the lacuna there should also have been the specification of the day of the week (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἡμέρ[ᾳ---]\u003C/span>).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 120 no.459 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 208 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>A with serif, squared Ε and Σ, cursive Μ, small O at l. 2. Small wavy line at l. 5 to indicate an abbreviation.\u003C/p> Lines 1-5  20-23  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[204,207,210,213,216,218,221,224,227],{"id":205,"html":206},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\">[ἐνθάδε]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"κῖτε\">[κῖτε]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"νος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"νος\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>νος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ζήσας\">ζή[σας]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἔτη\">[ἔτη\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀμέμπτως\">ἀμέμπ[τως]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"τελευτᾷ\">[τελευτᾷ]\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τῇ\">τῇ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"πρὸ\">πρὸ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\