03Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":208,"html":209},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003299_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003299_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003299.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003299-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":211,"html":212},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>Ferrua: [κεῖται]; Korhonen: [κῖτε]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 5\">line.5: \u003Cspan>In the lacuna, a day of the week should be mentioned\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":214,"html":215},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Here lies -nos, having lived for ... years blamelessly. He died 14 days before the kalends of March on the day of…\u003C/p>  ",{"id":214,"html":217},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Qui giace -nos, avendo vissuto ... anni senza colpa. Morì 14 giorni prima delle Calende di marzo, nel giorno di …\u003C/p>  ",{"id":219,"html":220},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>This Christian epitaph has the traditional structure with the \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐνθάδε κεῖται\u003C/span> formula, the name of the deceased (here in the lacuna) followed by his age and by another independent sentence with the day of death (with the present of \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω\u003C/span>), as recurring in other inscriptions from Catania, such as IG 14.556 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001375\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001375\u003C/a>. In the lacuna there should also have been the specification of the day of the week (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἡμέρ[ᾳ---]\u003C/span>).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":222,"html":223},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 120 no.459 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 208 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":225,"html":226},"handnote","\u003Cp>A with serif, squared Ε and Σ, cursive Μ, small O at l. 2. Small wavy line at l. 5 to indicate an abbreviation.\u003C/p> Lines 1-5  20-23  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":228,"html":229},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[231,233,236,237],{"html":232},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":234,"lang":121,"html":235},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\">[ἐνθάδε]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"κῖτε\">[κῖτε]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"νος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"νος\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan